{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"260fac5bcb","title":"关于团结党外军人问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b65577399","index":0,"year":1956,"month":11,"day":13,"articleId":"260fac5bcb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"b583f342c4","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东转发中国人民解放军第五十五军政治委员王振乾1956年10月29日关于团结该军军长陈明仁一起工作问题给广州军区党委的报告的批语。报告谈了军党委常委在同陈明仁相处中存在的缺点，以及为团结他一起工作采取的具体改进措施。通过相见以诚，多次找他个别息谈和集体交换意见，并改进领导制度，从而增强了团结。陈明仁表示对他帮助很大，希望今后大家常谈心。"},{"id":"473a6819ce","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7f5fe9ef9f","type":"title","text":"关于团结党外军人问题的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb"},{"id":"b583f342c4","type":"paragraph","text":"各同志阅。退彭德怀同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb"},{"id":"473a6819ce","type":"paragraph","text":"转发各军区、各军事学校以及有同样统战问题的军或师的党委阅读，加以讨论，仿照办理，认真解决团结党外军人问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb"},{"id":"a16f674d22","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb"},{"id":"366544d29f","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb"}],"page":{"id":"40d32f81b2","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"260fac5bcb","start":125,"end":125}}}},"__N_SSG":true}